Name: Name Change, P. O. John C. Williamson Corner, Queens
Title: A Local Law in relation to a corner name, P.O. John C. Williamson Corner, Borough of Queens.
BodyName: Parks, Recreation, Cultural Affairs, and International Intergroup Relations
Text:
Be it enacted by the Council as follows:


      Section 1.  The following corner name is hereby designated as hereafter indicated.


	New name			Present name			Limits


P.O. John C. Williamson 		(None)				the northwest corner of  Corner									80th Street and 34th Avenue



      ï¿½2.  This local law shall take effect immediately.
